T02D1601:118a-3: rdo rje phag mo phyag 'tshal te //
T02D1601:118a-4: lag pa'i mchod pa'i cho ga ni //
T02D1601:118a-5: lugs ni ji ltar yang dag bsdu //
T02D1601:118a-6: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la sogs pa'i dus su dpal
T02D1601:118a-7: 'khor lo sdom pa'i rnal 'byor dang ldan pa'i sngags
T02D1601:118a-8: pas / lag pa g-yon pa'i mthe bo dang /
T02D1601:118a-13: de rnams kyi sen mo rnams la rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
T02D1601:118a-18: don yod grub pa'i rang bzhin rnams so //
T02D1601:118a-19: go rims ji lta bar dkar po dang /
T02D1601:118b-2: nag po dang dmar ser dang /
T02D1601:118b-3: ljang gu'i kha dog rnams te /
T02D1601:118b-9: phat ham gi yi ge rnams bkod de /
T02D1601:118b-10: lag tu yang glo bur du grub pa'i padma dmar po 'dab ma lnga pa bsams te /
T02D1601:118b-11: shar la sogs pa'i 'dab ma rnams la g-yon skor gyis rim pa ji lta bar /
T02D1601:118b-27: ces bya ba'i sa bon gyi yi ge rnams blta'o //
T02D1601:118b-28: padma'i lte ba la rdo rje phag mo'i rang bzhin
T02D1601:118b-29: kha dog dmar po aom bam zhes bya ba'i sa
T02D1601:118b-30: bon te / 'di rnams kyi gzugs brnyan nam 'khor
T02D1601:118b-31: lo gsum gyi rgyab la yang yongs su gsal bar
T02D1601:118b-32: bon te / bya'o // de nas lag pa la gnas pas dang /
T02D1601:118b-40: gar gyi dbang phyug ma dang /
T02D1601:118b-41: padma 'bar ba rnams kyi rang bzhin du mos par bya'o //
T02D1601:118b-42: de nas lag pa la gnas pa'i sa bon de
T02D1601:118b-43: rnams la zhu ba'i rdzas kyis bsku ba byas la
T02D1601:118b-44: / lag pa'i mthil der dpa' bo dang /
T02D1601:118b-45: rnal 'byor mar byin gyis brlabs pa'i 'khor lo gsum
T02D1601:118b-46: gyi rang bzhin du mos pa byas la de zhu
T02D1601:118b-47: ba la sogs pa'i rdzas yi ge gsum gyis sam
T02D1601:118b-48: rkang ba brgyad pa'i dngags kyis dbul bar bya'o //
T02D1601:118b-49: de nas yang dag par mchod la lhag pa dang
T02D1601:118b-50: chad pa bskang pa'i phyir yi ge brgya pa bzlas
T02D1601:118b-51: par byas la 'khor lo byin gyis brlab pa la
T02D1601:118b-52: sogs pa'i don du gsol ba btab la /
T02D1601:118b-53: rdzas de gzhan nam gzhan du bzhag la /
T02D1601:118b-54: lag pa g-yon pa'i rdzas rnams kyis g-yon pa'i srin lag gis blangs pas snying ga dang /
T02D1601:118b-55: lce dang spyi bo la h'um a'a:aom zhes brjod pa sngon du 'gro bas bsku bar bya'o //
T02D1601:118b-56: de lha'i tshogs rnams bdag nyid la gzhug par mos par bya'o //
T02D1601:118b-58: kun du spyod pa dang 'brel pa ste /
